 UX researcher: my experience and things I’ve learned along the way</h1></div><div class="el"><div class="n em en eo ep"><div class="o n"><div><a href="/@tatiana.vlahovic?source=post_page-----906ab0bee087----------------------" rel="noopener"><div class="eq er es"><div class="et n eu o p s ev ew ex ey ez dk"><svg width="57" height="57" viewBox="0 0 57 57"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M28.5 1.2A27.45 27.45 0 0 0 4.06 15.82L3 15.27A28.65 28.65 0 0 1 28.5 0C39.64 0 49.29 6.2 54 15.27l-1.06.55A27.45 27.45 0 0 0 28.5 1.2zM4.06 41.18A27.45 27.45 0 0 0 28.5 55.8a27.45 27.45 0 0 0 24.44-14.62l1.06.55A28.65 28.65 0 0 1 28.5 57 28.65 28.65 0 0 1 3 41.73l1.06-.55z"></path></svg></div><img alt="Tatiana Vlahovic" class="r fa es er" src="https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/96/96/1*8KYF-FnVhBXUDf7WjICCwQ.jpeg" width="48" height="48"/></div></a></div><div class="fb ai r"><div class="n"><div style="flex:1"><span class="aq b ar as at au r dt q"><div class="fc n o fd"><span class="aq cl fe as br ff fg fh fi fj dt"><a href="/@tatiana.vlahovic?source=post_page-----906ab0bee087----------------------" class="cq cr az ba bb bc bd be bf bg fk bj bk fl fm" rel="noopener">Tatiana Vlahovic</a></span><div class="fn r an h"><a href="https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=register&amp;redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fuxdesign.cc%2Fbecoming-a-ux-researcher-my-experience-and-things-ive-learned-along-the-way-906ab0bee087&amp;source=-bb69650a981b-------------------------follow_byline-" class="fo dt q fp fq fr fs ft bg fl fu fv fw fx fy fz ga aq b ar gb cm au gc gd df ge gf bj" rel="noopener">Follow</a></div></div></span></div></div><span class="aq b ar as at au r av aw"><span class="aq cl fe as br ff fg fh fi fj av"><div><a class="cq cr az ba bb bc bd be bf bg fk bj bk fl fm" rel="noopener" href="/becoming-a-ux-researcher-my-experience-and-things-ive-learned-along-the-way-906ab0bee087?source=post_page-----906ab0bee087----------------------">Dec 24, 2017</a> <!-- -->·<!-- --> <!-- -->6<!-- --> min 